OL,3,CWhat is the difference between the
OL,4,Cpension triple lock and triple lock
OL,5,Cplus?
OL,7,FRishi Sunak has promised pensioners
OL,8,Fwill receive a tax break as part of an
OL,9,Fexpansion of the triple lock.
OL,11,FThe prime minister announced that from
OL,12,FApril next year, the income personal
OL,13,Fallowance for pensioners will be
OL,14,Fincreased in line with the triple
OL,15,Flock, as he continues the
OL,16,FConservatives' campaign.
OL,18,FBut what is the significance of this
OL,19,Fnew pledge, and what is the difference
OL,20,Fbetween the pensions triple lock and
OL,21,Fthe triple lock plus?
