OL,3,CWhat is the difference between the
OL,4,Cpension triple lock and triple lock
OL,5,Cplus?
OL,7,FWhat is the pensions triple lock?
OL,9,FThe triple lock guarantees the state
OL,10,Fpension grows every year in line with
OL,11,Finflation, with average UK earnings,
OL,12,For by at least 2.5% - whichever of the
OL,13,Fthree options is highest.
OL,15,FIn April 2024, the state pension went
OL,16,Fup by 8.5%.
OL,18,FThe policy helps to ensure pensioners'
OL,19,Fliving standards keep up with those of
OL,20,Fthe wider population.
