OL,5,Cplus?
OL,7,FHow does the State Pension work?
OL,9,FThe State Pension is a regular payment
OL,10,Ffrom the government people can receive
OL,11,Fwhen they reach a certain age.
OL,13,FState Pension age depends on your
OL,14,Fgender. Men born on or after April 6,
OL,15,F1951 and women born on or after April
OL,16,F6, 1953 are eligible.
OL,18,FHow much someone is paid depends on
OL,19,Ftheir National Insurance record. The
OL,20,Ffull amount of the new State Pension
OL,21,Fis #221.20 per week.
