OL,3,CWhat is the difference between the
OL,4,Cpension triple lock and triple lock
OL,5,Cplus?
OL,7,FWhat is the difference between the
OL,8,Ftriple lock and the triple lock plus?
OL,10,FThe triple lock plus will involve
OL,11,Ftaking the rules for the triple lock
OL,12,Fon state pensions, and applying them
OL,13,Fto pensioners' personal allowance too.
OL,15,FThis means, if elected, the
OL,16,FConservatives will increase personal
OL,17,Fallowance in line with whichever is
OL,18,Fhighest out of inflation, earnings, or
OL,19,Fby at least 2.5%.
