OL,3,CWhat is the difference between the
OL,4,Cpension triple lock and triple lock
OL,5,Cplus?
OL,7,FIn short - the amount of income you
OL,8,Fcan have in a year tax-free may go up.
OL,10,FHow much would the tax cut be worth?
OL,12,FThe Tories have said individual
OL,13,Fpensioners will save #275 by 2030 if
OL,14,Fthe plans come into place.
OL,16,FHow much could the policy cost?
OL,18,FThe policy is estimated to cost #2.4
OL,19,Fbillion a year by 2029/30.
