OL,3,CWhat is the difference between the
OL,4,Cpension triple lock and triple lock
OL,5,Cplus?
OL,7,FThe tax cut will be funded through a
OL,8,Fpreviously announced plan to raise #6
OL,9,Fbillion a year by the end of the next
OL,10,Fparliament by clamping down on tax
OL,11,Favoidance and evasion.
OL,13,FWhat has Labour said about the triple
OL,14,Flock?
OL,16,FLabour have committed to keeping the
OL,17,Ftriple lock, but said they would not
OL,18,Fmatch the new triple lock plus pledge.
